	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-172873816" class="story-title"> <a   href="//slashdot.org/story/24/01/27/0028235/bank-of-america-sends-warning-letters-to-employees-not-going-into-offices">Bank of America Sends Warning Letters To Employees Not Going Into Offices</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.theguardian.com/money/2024/jan/24/bank-of-america-warning-letters-return-to-offices"  title="External link - https://www.theguardian.com/money/2024/jan/24/bank-of-america-warning-letters-return-to-offices" target="_blank"> (theguardian.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
