	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64192954">The top comment is referring to this white paper. released this week by The Federal Reserve Bank of San Francisco:
<a href="https://www.frbsf.org/economic-research/publications/economic-letter/2024/january/does-working-from-home-boost-productivity-growth/" title="frbsf.org">https://www.frbsf.org/economic...</a> [frbsf.org]</div>
	</div>

