			<h4><a id="comment_link_64192312" name="comment_link_64192312" href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23206524&amp;cid=64192312" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64192312)" >Re:How to lose your best staff</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64192312" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64192312); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~JustAnotherOldGuy">JustAnotherOldGuy</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~JustAnotherOldGuy">( 4145623 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64192312">		
		on Saturday January 27, 2024 @10:51AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23206524&amp;cid=64192312">#64192312</a>)
